FormHelperFieldset
==================

Block method for creating the fieldset tag with or without a legend.


Example
=======

<% fieldset do %>
  <%= f.label :foo %>
  <%= f.text_field :foo %>
<% end %>

or

<% fieldset "Foo Options" do %>
  <%= f.label :foo %>
  <%= f.text_field :foo %>
<% end %>

